Package: zing
Version: 0.1.0
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Christopher Kelley <ckelley@ghostkellz.sh>
Depends: libc6
Recommends: git, tar, zstd
Homepage: https://github.com/ghostkellz/zing
Description: Next-generation build and packaging engine
 Zing is a lightning-fast, modern build and packaging engine
 written in Zig. It provides PKGBUILD compatibility, native
 Zig/C/C++ compilation, and cross-platform build support.
 .
 Features:
  - PKGBUILD compatible package building
  - Native Zig/C/C++ project compilation
  - Cross-compilation for multiple architectures
  - Fast parallel builds with intelligent caching
